</span><span class='line'>&lt;p>   12: astore $1
</span><span class='line'>   13: aload $1
</span><span class='line'>   14: invokestatic Outer$Inner.access$000 {(Outer$Inner) -> void}
</span><span class='line'>   17: return&lt;/p>
